::Striker::

Striker nods at Spears' answer, turning to look at Hot Rod.

"Not much," he says to the fellow Maximal, "We're thinking of launching an 
offensive against the Preds."

Striker glances at the Ark. "It might give them something to repair while we 
fix this dump."
